task.summary: Added code snippet to show how to open url in web browser.

XML parser added
InfoWindow for displaying detailed information about resource added
Fixed bug with layout of info window - now centred on map view.

Added 'resources with any' and 'resources with all' options for user selection
Added missing method specifications.
Added tests to cover methods added to Resource, ResourceRegistry and SelectionState classes.

Added JSON parser and corresponding data.
Added copy of tests in tests.faculty.model (for use on webCAT)
Added JXMapViewer2 license and corresponding GNU GPL v3 license.

Added more tests to deal with number format exceptions

Added more specific documentation for IResourceParser.parse
Modified specification of IResourceParser.parse so that it now throws IOException in addition to ResourceParserException and modified tests accordingly.
Modified UI to handle IOException.
Stripped out code that students must write during lab.
Removed calls to fail(...) from test templates
